timelineItems.name: MLS Chat
timelineItems.text: Robbie Keane already working out on the sideline 10 minutes into the game. #LAvHOU

timelineItems.name: Kyle Nowotny
timelineItems.text: Pinball in the box and fortunately Deric eventually smothers it. Surprised he didn't catch the initial cross. #LAGvHOU #ForeverOrange 13'

timelineItems.name: Andrea Canales
timelineItems.text: Dang, if Zardes had just reacted better to that Varynyn rebound, it might very well have been a Galaxy goal. #LAvHOU

timelineItems.name: Corner Of The Galaxy
timelineItems.text: Referee waves off the offside and Zardes flubs it. He needs to get those shots on goal. #LAGalaxy

timelineItems.name: Matt Pollard
timelineItems.text: LA has seen more of the ball since the Bruin breakaway. But their attack is like a chicken with its head cut off. #LAGalaxy #LAvHOU

timelineItems.name: neil ochotorena
timelineItems.text: Gyasi is really nobody without someone to spoon feed him a good through pass. #lagalaxy

timelineItems.name: Adam Serrano
timelineItems.text: The #LAGalaxy are certainly the better team right now, but they're just lacking that final pass in the last third of the field.

timelineItems.name: Andrea Canales
timelineItems.text: Oscar Sorto ran right into a Houston defender early on, but since then, the youngster has done fine. (jinxing him, I'm sure). #LAvHOU

timelineItems.name: Corner Of The Galaxy
timelineItems.text: Some good movement already with Jose Villarreal keeping possession on the left and firing a great ball across the field. #LAGalaxy #LAvHOU

timelineItems.name: C. Maxwell
timelineItems.text: Should have been a yellow and a PK, instead we got a red and FK ten yards outside the box #LAvHOU

timelineItems.desc: The LA Galaxy and Houston Dynamo meet for a second time this season when the Western Conference clubs face off in the second match on Viernes de Fútbol at StubHub Center.
timelineItems.title: HIGHLIGHTS: LA Galaxy vs Houston Dynamo | May 22, 2015
